<br>
Please do not reinstate in any way the old alignment system.<br>
<br>
If you do create a new alignment system, please make it realistic, self correcting, GM alterable/customizable, faction-based, and fun-promoting.<br>
<br>
Please do not let intolerant, stick-in-the-mud people re-ruin this server or return it to the prejudice simulator that it was before the May 8 patch.<br>
