<br>
So, as part of my character's role, as a follower of Karana, he doesn't hate anyone.  Does Karana choose not to rain on lands where evil characters live?  Am I not allowed to choose my own friends, or is it more of a &quot;roleplay&quot; feature that I allow Verant to choose who I may group with?<br>
